OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775203520
OL,3,C'Not our King' sprayed onto cathedral
OL,4,Cin escalation of campaign against
OL,5,Cmonarchy
OL,7,FCampaigners from the group Republic
OL,8,Fhave become much more vocal and
OL,9,Fvisible in recent years, but the
OL,10,Fspraying of graffiti on an historic
OL,11,Fcathedral suggests a more aggressive
OL,12,Fapproach from some who wish to have
OL,13,Fthe monarchy abolished.
OL,15,FRed graffiti spelling out the words
OL,16,F"Not Our King" was sprayed onto the
OL,17,Fperimeter wall of St Asaph Cathedral
OL,18,Fin north Wales, shortly before an
OL,19,FEaster service there attended by King
OL,20,FCharles and Queen Camilla.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
