FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775203520
OL,3,C'Not our King' sprayed onto cathedral
OL,4,Cin escalation of campaign against
OL,5,Cmonarchy
OL,7,FIt is not known who sprayed the
OL,8,Fgraffiti, and Republic said it did not
OL,9,Fcondone the action.
OL,11,FThe Royal Maundy service is held at a
OL,12,Fdifferent location around the country
OL,13,Feach year on the Thursday before
OL,14,FEaster.
OL,16,FThis was the first time the monarch
OL,17,Fhas travelled to a Welsh cathedral on
OL,18,FMaundy Thursday since 1982.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775203520
OL,3,C'Not our King' sprayed onto cathedral
OL,4,Cin escalation of campaign against
OL,5,Cmonarchy
OL,7,FWorkers in hi-vis jackets were seen
OL,8,Fattempting to remove the spray paint
OL,9,Fbefore the King and Queen arrived.
OL,11,FIn the end, it was covered up with a
OL,12,Ftarpaulin sheet and a police van was
OL,13,Fparked in front of it.
OL,15,FIt's not known if the King and Queen
OL,16,Fsaw the graffiti or were made aware of
OL,17,Fit before their arrival, but they
OL,18,Fwould have heard the official protest
OL,19,Ffrom the Republic campaigners, who now
OL,20,Fgather at this event each year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775203520
OL,3,C'Not our King' sprayed onto cathedral
OL,4,Cin escalation of campaign against
OL,5,Cmonarchy
OL,7,FThey brought their yellow flags and
OL,8,Fbanners and chanted "Charles, what did
OL,9,Fyou know?", which is related to the
OL,10,Fongoing investigation into Andrew
OL,11,FMountbatten-Windsor and his long
OL,12,Ffriendship with the convicted sex
OL,13,Foffender Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,15,FThe chief executive of Republic,
OL,16,FGraham Smith said: "Charles shouldn't
OL,17,Fbe able to avoid questions about his
OL,18,Fcomplicity in the Andrew scandal. The
OL,19,Fpublic wants answers. That's why
OL,20,Factivists were protesting in North
OL,21,FWales today."
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@JO]
