OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775203520
OL,3,C'Not our King' sprayed onto cathedral
OL,4,Cin escalation of campaign against
OL,5,Cmonarchy
OL,7,FAsked by ITV News for a response to
OL,8,Fthe graffiti sprayed on the cathedral,
OL,9,FSmith said he and the fellow
OL,10,Fprotestors "do not condone graffiti,
OL,11,Fbut it says something about changing
OL,12,Fattitudes that it would happen in a
OL,13,Fsmall place like St Asaph."
OL,26,@rD@LOUuD@[O]
