OL,3,C'Not our King' sprayed onto cathedral
OL,4,Cin escalation of campaign against
OL,5,Cmonarchy
OL,7,FNorth Wales Police said in a
OL,8,Fstatement: "We are investigating an
OL,9,Fincident of criminal damage in the
OL,10,Farea surrounding St Asaph Cathedral.
OL,11,FGraffiti appeared on the outside
OL,12,Fsurrounding walls in areas open to the
OL,13,Fpublic during the early hours of
OL,14,Ftoday, 2 April. Denbighshire Council
OL,15,Fare in the process of removing the
OL,16,Fgraffiti."
OL,26,@xD@JO]
