OL,3,C'Not our King' sprayed onto cathedral
OL,4,Cin escalation of campaign against
OL,5,Cmonarchy
OL,7,FChief Inspector Caroline Mullen-Hurst
OL,8,Ffrom the force added: "Officers are
OL,9,Fconducting enquiries to establish the
OL,10,Ffull circumstances and to identify the
OL,11,Findividual or offenders responsible.
OL,12,FSuch behaviour has no place in our
OL,13,Fcommunity, and we are committed to
OL,14,Fensuring that those responsible are
OL,15,Fheld accountable."
OL,17,FThe first recorded Royal Maundy
OL,18,Fservice was held in 1210 by King John
OL,19,Fand commemorates the Last Supper of
OL,20,FJesus Christ.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
