OL,3,C'Not our King' sprayed onto cathedral
OL,4,Cin escalation of campaign against
OL,5,Cmonarchy
OL,7,FIt set off a tradition of distributing
OL,8,Falms by the monarch.
OL,10,FThis year, King Charles gave
OL,11,Frecipients two purses: a white one
OL,12,Fincluding a set of specially minted
OL,13,Fsilver Maundy coins totalling 77
OL,14,Fpennies, to match the King's age; a
OL,15,Fred purse containing a #5 coin marking
OL,16,F100 years since the late Queen's birth
OL,17,Fand a 50p coin celebrating the 50th
OL,18,Fanniversary of The King's Trust
OL,19,Fcharity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
