OL,3,C'Not our King' sprayed onto cathedral
OL,4,Cin escalation of campaign against
OL,5,Cmonarchy
OL,7,FThe Royal Family will next gather over
OL,8,Fthe bank holiday weekend for the
OL,9,FEaster Matins Service at St. George's
OL,10,FChapel in Windsor on Sunday.
OL,12,FThe King and Queen will attend with
OL,13,Fother members of the family, but the
OL,14,Fpalace has said the daughters of the
OL,15,Fformer prince Andrew, Princesses
OL,16,FBeatrice and Eugenie, will not be
OL,17,Fthere as they have made alternative
OL,18,Fplans with the agreement and
OL,19,Funderstanding of the King.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
